caption.p: Electrochemical impedance spectroscopy of ( a) C/SiO 2-0.04 M, C/SiO 2-0.055 M, and C/SiO 2-0.085 M, uncalendered electrodes before cycling; ( b) C/SiO 2-0.04 M, C/SiO 2-0.055 M, and C/SiO 2-0.085 M, uncalendered electrodes after cycling; ( c) C/SiO 2-0.04 M, C/SiO 2-0.055 M, and C/SiO 2-0.085 M, calendered electrodes before cycling; ( d) C/SiO 2-0.04 M, C/SiO 2-0.055 M, and C/SiO 2-0.085 M, calendered electrodes after cycling; ( e) The equivalent circuit of the C/SiO 2-0.085 M uncalendered electrode after 200 cycles.
